high_descs: turn left to face the bathroom sink
pick up the wash cloth above the soap
face the sink while carrying the wash cloth in hand
place the wash cloth in the sink and turn on the water to fill the sink, the turn off the water and remove the wash cloth
carry the cloth and face the drawer below the sink to the far right
place the wash cloth in the drawer and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Clean a wash cloth in the sink and store it in a drawer

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the vanity.
Pick up the red cloth on the counter to the left of the sink.
Move to your right and face the sink.
Put the red rag in the sink, rinse it off, then take it out.
Take the rag out of the sink and turn around.
Put the rag in the vanity drawer to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a clean red rag in the right hand vanity drawer.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the counter.
Pick the red cloth up from the counter.
Move to the right and face the sink.
Put the cloth in the sink, turn the water on and then off and take the cloth out of the sink.
Move to the right of the sink.
Open the drawer on the right and put the cloth in and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean cloth in a drawer.
